                </div>
                <div class="panel-body lead">
                    <div class="panel-body-text">
                  You can copy a passage by clicking “cite” for a bookmarked passage in the Bookmarks Bar. This will place a new passage in the current view with you as the author and the original listed as a source. You can also add sources to existing posts by clicking “add source” in the edit view.
              </div>
                  <!-- <button class="btn btn-primary">Find Awesome People</button> -->
